/company/?scode=6954" data-track-article-link="true">Fanuc</a>和<a href="https://www.nikkei.com/nkd/company/?scode=6506" data-track-article-link="true">Yaskawa Electric</a>继续保持低价。</p><p class="paragraph_p15tm1hb"> [日经快讯 (NQN)]</p> ]]>;</description><pubDate> Wed, 17 May 2023 04:05:07 GMT</pubDate><guid ispermalink="false"> https://www.nikkei.com/article/DGXZASS0ISS14_X10C23A5000000/</guid><link/> https://www.nikkei.com/article/DGXZASS0ISS14_X10C23A5000000/<category>国内股票概况</category><category>库存</category></item><item><title><![CDATA[鳥型ロボが水田の雑草抑制 宮崎・延岡市でスマート稲作]]></title><description><![CDATA[<figure class="center_c1symtaw figure_f1xkd112 figure_fv30jf" data-image-viewer-target="true" data-src-for-image-viewer="https://article-image-ix.nikkei.com/https%3A%2F%2Fimgix-proxy.n8s.jp%2FDSXZQO3352878016052023000000-2.jpg?ixlib=js-3.8.0&amp;w=680&amp;h=425&amp;auto=format%2Ccompress&amp;fit=crop&amp;bg=FFFFFF&amp;s=21dd0fa0f769bea6a9a2ad64c2828f59"><div class="pictureWrapper_p13ffdka" style="max-width:638px"><div style="max-width:638px"><picture class="picture_p169s49k" style="padding-bottom:62.539184952978054%;width:638px"><source srcset="https://article-image-ix.nikkei.com/https%3A%2F%2Fimgix-proxy.n8s.jp%2FDSXZQO3352878016052023000000-2.jpg?ixlib=js-3.8.0&amp;w=638&amp;h=399&amp;auto=format%2Ccompress&amp;fit=crop&amp;bg=FFFFFF&amp;s=35e94944c43e2222bb91a95e2ab33fe2" media="(min-width: 1232px)"><source srcset="https://article-image-ix.nikkei.com/https%3A%2F%2Fimgix-proxy.n8s.jp%2FDSXZQO3352878016052023000000-2.jpg?ixlib=js-3.8.0&amp;w=638&amp;h=399&amp;auto=format%2Ccompress&amp;fit=crop&amp;bg=FFFFFF&amp;s=35e94944c43e2222bb91a95e2ab33fe2" media="(min-width: 992px)"><source srcset="https://article-image-ix.nikkei.com/https%3A%2F%2Fimgix-proxy.n8s.jp%2FDSXZQO3352878016052023000000-2.jpg?ixlib=js-3.8.0&amp;w=600&amp;h=375&amp;auto=format%2Ccompress&amp;fit=crop&amp;bg=FFFFFF&amp;s=bd386a5bc85737485d655de00f5fa107" media="(min-width: 752px)"><source srcset="https://article-image-ix.nikkei.com/https%3A%2F%2Fimgix-proxy.n8s.jp%2FDSXZQO3352878016052023000000-2.jpg?ixlib=js-3.8.0&amp;w=600&amp;h=375&amp;auto=format%2Ccompress&amp;fit=crop&amp;bg=FFFFFF&amp;s=bd386a5bc85737485d655de00f5fa107" media="(min-width: 316px)"><source srcset="https://article-image-ix.nikkei.com/https%3A%2F%2Fimgix-proxy.n8s.jp%2FDSXZQO3352878016052023000000-2.jpg?ixlib=js-3.8.0&amp;w=600&amp;h=375&amp;auto=format%2Ccompress&amp;fit=crop&amp;bg=FFFFFF&amp;s=bd386a5bc85737485d655de00f5fa107" media="(min-width: 0px)"><img loading="lazy" class="image_i6zn6lo" src="https://article-image-ix.nikkei.com/https%3A%2F%2Fimgix-proxy.n8s.jp%2FDSXZQO3352878016052023000000-2.jpg?ixlib=js-3.8.0&amp;w=638&amp;h=399&amp;auto=format%2Ccompress&amp;fit=crop&amp;bg=FFFFFF&amp;s=35e94944c43e2222bb91a95e2ab33fe2" alt="" title="" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></picture></div><div class="footer_f1d0ecpb"><figcaption class="caption_c1iimty1">鸟形机器人控制杂草远程监控稻田</figcaption></div></div></figure><p class="paragraph_p15tm1hb">在宫崎县延冈市开始了一项旨在使用机器人进行“智能水稻种植”的示范实验。无人机被用于在稻田中直接播种水稻种子，鸟形机器人控制杂草生长并远程监控。今后，我们还将开发执行收获工作的机器人，并在所有过程中促进省力化。</p><p class="paragraph_p15tm1hb"> 2022 年 12 月，宫崎县延冈市与机器人开发商 tmsuk（京都市）签署了一项合作协议，以研究和开发使用机器人的水稻种植。示范工程将在全市3000平方米水田中实施。 </p><figure class="center_c1symtaw figure_f1xkd112 figure_fv30jf" data-image-viewer-target="true" data-src-for-image-viewer="https://article-image-ix.nikkei.com/https%3A%2F%2Fimgix-proxy.n8s.jp%2FDSXZQO3352848016052023000000-1.jpg?ixlib=js-3.8.0&amp;w=680&amp;h=382&amp;auto=format%2Ccompress&amp;fit=crop&amp;bg=FFFFFF&amp;s=82003ef0ec31a91751f4849966151bc9"><div class="pictureWrapper_p13ffdka" style="max-width:638px"><div style="max-width:638px"><picture class="picture_p169s49k" style="padding-bottom:56.26959247648903%;width:638px"><source srcset="https://article-image-ix.nikkei.com/https%3A%2F%2Fimgix-proxy.n8s.jp%2FDSXZQO3352848016052023000000-1.jpg?ixlib=js-3.8.0&amp;w=638&amp;h=359&amp;auto=format%2Ccompress&amp;fit=crop&amp;bg=FFFFFF&amp;s=641b4a4bf388c5ecd86f755efd345d1a" media="(min-width: 1232px)"><source srcset="https://article-image-ix.nikkei.com/https%3A%2F%2Fimgix-proxy.n8s.jp%2FDSXZQO3352848016052023000000-1.jpg?ixlib=js-3.8.0&amp;w=638&amp;h=359&amp;auto=format%2Ccompress&amp;fit=crop&amp;bg=FFFFFF&amp;s=641b4a4bf388c5ecd86f755efd345d1a" media="(min-width: 992px)"><source srcset="https://article-image-ix.nikkei.com/https%3A%2F%2Fimgix-proxy.n8s.jp%2FDSXZQO3352848016052023000000-1.jpg?ixlib=js-3.8.0&amp;w=600&amp;h=337&amp;auto=format%2Ccompress&amp;fit=crop&amp;bg=FFFFFF&amp;s=62d80820fd758cf1fa484d1d26983c6c" media="(min-width: 752px)"><source srcset="https://article-image-ix.nikkei.com/https%3A%2F%2Fimgix-proxy.n8s.jp%2FDSXZQO3352848016052023000000-1.jpg?ixlib=js-3.8.0&amp;w=600&amp;h=337&amp;auto=format%2Ccompress&amp;fit=crop&amp;bg=FFFFFF&amp;s=62d80820fd758cf1fa484d1d26983c6c" media="(min-width: 316px)"><source srcset="https://article-image-ix.nikkei.com/https%3A%2F%2Fimgix-proxy.n8s.jp%2FDSXZQO3352848016052023000000-1.jpg?ixlib=js-3.8.0&amp;w=600&amp;h=337&amp;auto=format%2Ccompress&amp;fit=crop&amp;bg=FFFFFF&amp;s=62d80820fd758cf1fa484d1d26983c6c" media="(min-width: 0px)"><img loading="lazy" class="image_i6zn6lo" src="https://article-image-ix.nikkei.com/https%3A%2F%2Fimgix-proxy.n8s.jp%2FDSXZQO3352848016052023000000-1.jpg?ixlib=js-3.8.0&amp;w=638&amp;h=359&amp;auto=format%2Ccompress&amp;fit=crop&amp;bg=FFFFFF&amp;s=641b4a4bf388c5ecd86f755efd345d1a" alt="" title="" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></picture></div><div class="footer_f1d0ecpb"><figcaption class="caption_c1iimty1">无人机在稻田中直接播种水稻（宫崎县延冈市16日）</figcaption></div></div></figure><p class="paragraph_p15tm1hb">涂有氧化铁的种子更容易沉入水中，由无人机直接播种。鸟形机器人“雷鸟一号”的灵感来自养鸭方式，用鳍状肢搅水抑制杂草。此外，还将安装自动测量水位、水温、风速、降雨量等的传感器，收集一年多的数据。还建立了远程控制供水和停水系统。</p><p class="paragraph_p15tm1hb">未来，我们将着手开发可以收割水稻的机器人，并在三年内建立一个使用机器人的水稻生产系统。 tmsuk 董事长兼首席执行官 Yoichi Takamoto 表示：“我们希望通过用很少的劳动力种植水稻来为防止废弃农田的扩大做出贡献。”</p><div class="container_ci59o1r"><p class="title_t1guwbqo"> 【相关文章】</p><ul class="l